{"tid":1614000,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌醒你班開街井","createTime":"2019-10-02T16:22:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T15:24:49.000Z","uid":326205,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f214c2563bcc45766d2ec12416aa66550d5e7682","tid":1614000,"uid":326205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:22:21.000Z","msg":"等我屌醒你哋，紅色街井既水係淡水，黨鐵只要抽走D水，抹兩抹，乜事都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n千其唔好<strong>開黃色既街井</strong>入面係咸水，入左黨鐵會一陣味，又會浸壞同氧化金屬物品<br />\n<br />\n千其唔好咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有街井開關位置都印係街井頂，藍色代表果個頭冇水出<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"943c65dff5431a327c921ea7236656885dd2947e","tid":1614000,"uid":1654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:22:40.000Z","msg":"好難搵黃色喇"},{"pid":"56484169d7232fe50f0b19191102917ea3f6894f","tid":1614000,"uid":290977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:22:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b75ee66098909dcc576fdab7ce8014e45c9aedb","tid":1614000,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:24:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fd66d11b9d204bb8d381ce7257917cd656ebd432","tid":1614000,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:28:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"787c91de6d20583e69d0101a453fc28d69fd4b71","tid":1614000,"uid":267909,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:36:36.000Z","msg":"重有見黃色架咩，細果時都少見"},{"pid":"cd4efd556ff58d112f35c02c92a6cac538521e30",